288
00:30:20,544 --> 00:30:22,512
Ah, it'll be light in an hour.

289
00:30:25,049 --> 00:30:27,415
He'll never do it then.

290
00:30:27,518 --> 00:30:29,918
I say we give him
his opportunity now.

291
00:30:33,691 --> 00:30:35,591
All units, this is Charlie One.

