305
00:31:54,672 --> 00:31:56,572
I thought it was the guy.
We all did.

306
00:31:56,674 --> 00:31:58,574
What if it was, James?

307
00:31:58,676 --> 00:32:01,270
Is bouncing the subject's head
off the hood of the car...

308
00:32:01,378 --> 00:32:04,347
gonna do anything to change all
the other murders that will occur today?

309
00:32:04,448 --> 00:32:07,679
Come on, Frank! Some guy cut your wife
and your daughter into eight pieces...

310
00:32:07,785 --> 00:32:09,810
and you just stand there
and read him his rights?

311
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:13,083
He hasn't killed our wives or our families,
and he's not going to.

312
00:32:13,190 --> 00:32:16,284
If you make every one of these personal,
you'll go insane.

313
00:32:16,393 --> 00:32:19,885
And that's from having
been there, James.

314
00:32:22,366 --> 00:32:24,766
I get so far into the heads
of the killers and the victims.

315
00:32:24,869 --> 00:32:27,702
- You haven't got there at all.
- Don't you tell me where I am!

316
00:32:27,805 --> 00:32:29,796
You put them in your head.

317
00:32:33,644 --> 00:32:36,670
I keep reliving...

318
00:32:36,781 --> 00:32:39,045
what it's like
to be cut in half...

319
00:32:39,150 --> 00:32:41,050
or four or eight.

320
00:32:41,152 --> 00:32:44,815
This isn't about you, James.
The whole thing.

321
00:32:44,922 --> 00:32:46,822
What's goin' on out here.

322
00:32:46,924 --> 00:32:50,223
It's about us.
Me. You.

323
00:32:50,327 --> 00:32:53,558
The killer
and the victim.

324
00:32:57,168 --> 00:33:00,899
I can't help
but take this personally.

325
00:33:01,005 --> 00:33:03,337
Another person is
going to die, horribly...

326
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:07,206
because Is--
we screwed up.

327
00:33:07,311 --> 00:33:11,008
I-- we did all this
for nothing.

328
00:33:11,115 --> 00:33:14,346
No, we didn't.

329
00:33:14,451 --> 00:33:18,717
We handed out 30 pins
from the hospital charity to be placed here.

330
00:33:22,326 --> 00:33:24,726
There's 31 .

331
