and eyeglass labs around the area.

335
00:34:08,873 --> 00:34:11,501
Plus, a resident four blocks
from the hospital...

336
00:34:11,609 --> 00:34:14,908
recalls seeing an orange van driving around
the area the night of the memorial.

337
00:34:15,012 --> 00:34:17,674
Yeah.

338
00:34:23,587 --> 00:34:27,819
A saleslady from one of those
eyeglass places in Woodburn...

339
00:34:27,925 --> 00:34:31,554
- recalls one of the suspects from the flyer.
- Which one did she recall?

340
00:34:32,863 --> 00:34:35,889
- This guy.
- Are you sure?

341
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:39,436
Oh, yeah. Yeah, I remember.
He was a total ass.

342
00:34:39,536 --> 00:34:42,528
- In what way?
- just real attitude.

343
00:34:42,640 --> 00:34:45,837
He even had trouble
taking a number like everybody else.

344
00:34:45,943 --> 00:34:50,607
- He needed one lens replaced. The left lens?
